The paper deals with a new width measure for tree decomposition and its applications to various problems in graph theory and hypergraph theory. The paper also discusses the construction of decomposition and the time complexity of the problem. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
